author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Deutsche Telekom earns 400 mln eur from Scout24 IPO
text:
Oct 2 Deutsche Telekom AG
* Will continue to hold 14 percent of Scout24, before greenshoe option
* Gross proceeds of 400 million eur from Scout24 IPO before greenshoe option
* Has generated total proceeds of 2.1 billion eur from the sale of Scout24 shares Further company coverage:
